===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|青|爭|ls=psc|c1=p|c2=p}}. Note that {{och-l|*青}} is also a compound with two phonetic components.

{{Shuowen}} interprets {{och-l|*青|blue}} as a semantic component.

===Etymology===
Perhaps from {{der|zh|mkh}}; compare {{cog|okz|siṅ||to stay in/at; to abide; to be still}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). {{och-l|靖}} is the same word ([[ibid.]]).

